---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Real Estate Agent Carina Brisbane | Daniel Gierach"
  description="Daniel Gierach, real estate agent in Carina Brisbane. Family suburb with strong fundamentals and growing buyer demand. Ray White Bulimba. Call 0412 523 821."
>

<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Real Estate Agent Carina Brisbane",
  "description": "Daniel Gierach is a specialist real estate agent in Carina Brisbane, serving the inner-east corridor.",
  "url": "https://www.danielgierach.com/suburbs/carina",
  "breadcrumb": {
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://www.danielgierach.com" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Carina", "item": "https://www.danielgierach.com/suburbs/carina" }
    ]
  }
})}</script>

<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is the median house price in Carina?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Carina's median house price is approximately $1 million as of early 2026. The suburb offers a practical combination of family-sized blocks, post-war homes and newer builds at pricing that remains accessible compared to closer-in eastern suburbs." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How long does it take to sell a home in Carina?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Well-priced Carina properties typically sell within 30 to 45 days. The suburb attracts a consistent buyer pool of families and first-home buyers, particularly those seeking larger blocks than are available in pricier nearby suburbs." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is Carina like as a place to live?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Carina is a quiet, family-oriented suburb with access to Carindale Westfield, Belmont Hills bushland and Runcorn Road's local shops. It has good public transport options and is popular with buyers seeking a suburban lifestyle within a 10-kilometre radius of the CBD." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is Carina a good suburb to buy in right now?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Carina continues to attract steady demand as buyers look for affordability without sacrificing access to the inner east. Values have grown consistently as price momentum from more expensive neighbouring suburbs has spread outward through the eastern corridor." }
    }
  ]
})}</script>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 1: HERO
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:#1c1917; color:#f2efe9; padding: 100px 24px 80px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Carina</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:1.5rem; color:#f2efe9;">
      Real Estate Agent<br/><em style="color:#f5d07a;">Carina.</em>
    </h1>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4bc; max-width:580px; margin:0 auto 2.5rem;">
      Specialist property sales in Carina and Brisbane's inner east.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/listings" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">View Current Listings</a>
      <a href="/property-worth" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">What's Your Property Worth?</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 2: WHY THIS AREA
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Family living with strong fundamentals.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Carina offers a compelling mix of value, lifestyle and accessibility. Its quiet streets, good schools and proximity to the CBD make it consistently popular with families and owner-occupiers looking for long-term value.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I work closely with buyers active in Carina and the surrounding suburbs, which means I understand the demand drivers and how to position your home for maximum competition.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Belmont Road is Carina's main spine, providing easy access to Wynnum Road and the eastern freeway network for buyers who commute or value connectivity. The Carina Leagues Club on Creek Road is a well-used community hub and one of the social anchors that gives the suburb its established, grounded feel. Sporting facilities including the cricket and football grounds at Clem Jones Centre are a genuine drawcard for active family buyers. Demand has been particularly strong from buyers downsizing from larger homes in nearby Camp Hill and Carindale, drawn to Carina's value proposition and walkable streetscape.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Carina Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Inner-east Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Family Suburb</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Strong fundamentals</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/cannon-hill" style="color:#c4912a;">Cannon Hill</a>, <a href="/suburbs/carina-heights" style="color:#c4912a;">Carina Heights</a>, <a href="/suburbs/carindale" style="color:#c4912a;">Carindale</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION: FAQ
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">FAQ</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Carina.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the median house price in Carina?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Carina's median house price is approximately $1 million as of early 2026. The suburb offers a practical combination of family-sized blocks, post-war homes and newer builds at pricing that remains accessible compared to closer-in eastern suburbs.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Carina?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Carina properties typically sell within 30 to 45 days. The suburb attracts a consistent buyer pool of families and first-home buyers, particularly those seeking larger blocks than are available in pricier nearby suburbs.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is Carina like as a place to live?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Carina is a quiet, family-oriented suburb with access to Carindale Westfield, Belmont Hills bushland and Runcorn Road's local shops. It has good public transport options and is popular with buyers seeking a suburban lifestyle within a 10-kilometre radius of the CBD.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Carina a good suburb to buy in right now?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Carina continues to attract steady demand as buyers look for affordability without sacrificing access to the inner east. Values have grown consistently as price momentum from more expensive neighbouring suburbs has spread outward through the eastern corridor.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

